name: Going Away
description:
Dear customers:
Sinclaire Muse is taking some time off to travel around the world to look for inspirations and to source unique materials.
Our web-store is currently unavailable for purchase within this period, but some of our statement necklaces are available for sale at MERGE fashion boutique in Subiaco. 

Love from
Sinclaire Muse
